com.hurence.logisland.logging

Interface ProcessorLog

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentLog

    public interface ProcessorLog
extends ComponentLog
    The ProcessorLog is an extension of ComponentLog but provides no additional functionality. It exists because ProcessorLog was created first, but when Controller Services and Reporting Tasks began to be used more heavily loggers were needed for them as well. We did not want to return a ProcessorLog to a ControllerService or a ReportingTask, so all of the methods were moved to a higher interface named ComponentLog. However, we kept the ProcessorLog interface around in order to maintain backward compatibility.
